OL,3,CTwo injured after knifeman threatens
OL,4,Cpeople on street
OL,6,FTwo people have been injured by a
OL,7,Fknifeman threatening people on a
OL,8,Fstreet in Brighton.
OL,10,FSussex Police responded to a report of
OL,11,Fa man with a knife in Sillwood Road,
OL,12,FBrighton, on Saturday evening, 27 June
OL,13,F2026.
OL,15,FTwo members of the public were
OL,16,Fassaulted during the incident, which
OL,17,Fwas reported just before 6pm.
OL,19,FOne of the men assaulted was treated
OL,20,Fin hospital and released, for serious
OL,21,Fbut non-life threatening injuries.
