OL,3,CTwo injured after knifeman threatens
OL,4,Cpeople on street
OL,6,FThe man with the knife, who lives
OL,7,Flocally, was swiftly tackled to the
OL,8,Fground by members of the public and a
OL,9,Fknife was seized.
OL,11,FA 33-year-old local man has been
OL,12,Farrested for assault occasioning
OL,13,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent and
OL,14,Fhe is in custody.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Jen Pietersen
OL,17,Fsaid: "This was a distressing incident
OL,18,Ffor those in the vicinity.
